(20329, 'Chinese Contemporary Craftsmanship Exhibition, Beijing, 2012', '<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">In 2012-2013, SHANG XIA will be exploring the theme of In&middot;Out. The two complementary elements of In&middot;Out will engage, balance and evolve in areas of technique, material and color. To coincide with the opening of its Beijing Boutique, SHANG XIA presents the Chinese Contemporary Craftsmanship Exhibition, showcasing new creations and new craft techniques for furniture, tea tables, clothing and jewellery.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	A classical courtyard in the heart of the Beijing maelstrom. A droplet of calm and elegance, like the gardens of Suzhou. Using the tools of space and solidity, light and shade, SHANG XIA will create here a modern space inspired by the five senses. Here, SHANG XIA craftsmen will demonstrate the art of cashmere felt and bamboo weaving. In a gracious tea space and incense space, the natural light and shade of a bamboo grove convey the pleasure of a lifestyle which combines heaven and earth; the inner and the outer; tradition and modernity; man and nature; simplicity and elegance.</p>\n<p class="p2">\n	Wind - Tea Space</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">Part the bamboo fronds and step around the Taihu rock; hidden inside them is the Wind tea space. Hollow bamboos clink in the wind, a constant musical accompaniment. Let petty irritations dissolve in the breeze and the play of light and shade, while the aroma of tea leaves you at peace, in space between heaven and earth.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	Cloud &ndash; Incense Space</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">In classical Chinese architecture, the Dougong is a key element, supporting the superstructure of the building. Inspired by the unique craft and form of the Dougong, SHANG XIA reproduces the Dougong form in bamboo in this incense space. The lazy twists of smoke and the soft fragrance offer peace and pleasure; a moment out of samsara.</span></p>\n', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-07 19:01:06', '2014-09-17 23:21:50', NULL, 1, 'news', 0, NULL),
