(20396, 'LEADER', 'Created from black or tea-colored cotton these garments are carefully finished. The 3-piece set composed of a traditional Chinese suit and a long, English-style outer jacket. \n\nNostalgic of eras gone by, the seams are uniquely finished with Jali stitching (reticulated carved and ornamental work), allowing the fabric to breathe. - A perfect accessory for a rainy day.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-09 23:40:17', '2014-09-17 20:15:23', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
