(20398, 'DRAGON PEARL', 'Since ancient times in China, the dragon chasing a “flaming pearl” has been a symbol of imperial power and authority. Inspired from this long tradition, the SHANG XIA Dragon Pearl collection of earrings, necklaces, pendants and bracelets integrates the concept of “up” and “down” with the pearl, continually running forward, perpetually evolving.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-09 23:40:18', '2014-09-17 20:15:22', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
