(20434, 'GARDEN', 'The SHANG XIA Garden collection includes pendants of Zitan, white jade, agate, gold, silver – and, of course, original Taihu Rock, prized over the ages for representing wisdom and immortality. They twist and turn, intriguing and wild, solid and hollow, a surprising form from every side and angle. The Zitan, jade, agate and Taihu Rock are hand selected and carved in a process taking up to 300 hours. The Garden collection brings the same sense of the contemplative meditation which inspired ancient philosophers and poets to a single tiny pendant to be worn over your heart, inspiring your soul.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-09 23:40:23', '2014-09-17 20:15:20', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
