(20436, 'SHAN SHUI', 'Jade and agate, glossy and heartfelt, uncommon treasures revealing a fineness of grain that flows like water. The Shan Shui jewelry collection features breathtaking pendants, earrings and brooches, all painstakingly carved and elegantly wrought in white jade, black jade, moss agate, smoky agate and black jade. These precious stones have been carved and polished in the form of an ancient Chinese bi coin, a 2mm thick circle with an emblematic inner square cutout. The Shan Shui collection has been created by a master craftsman spending some 480 hours in the rendering of each piece. The exact design method requires the jade or agate to be spun, cut and polished on a polishing wheel, a process representing samsāra – the ever-turning wheel of life. With their natural materials, each Shan Shui piece possesses its own singular pattern, and makes a magnificent gift or prized addition to one’s own fine jewelry collection.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-09 23:40:23', '2014-09-17 20:15:20', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
