(20439, 'Tian Ti', 'Tian Ti, in Chinese means ladder to heaven. Inspired by the cooling bamboo undershirts worn in summer in traditional China SHANG XIA Tian Ti collection of jewelry comes in Hotan jade, Zitan, gold-plated silver and gold with diamond. Comprised of narrow tubes with walls just 0.35mm thick and crafted by hand into a chain. Every link has been polished inside and out to a shining finish. The Hotan jade and Zitan items were carved, link by link, entirely by hand, requiring 400 to 900 hours of incredible skill for each individual piece. The texture of each material gives the individual pieces their own character: jade is clean and smooth; Zitan is natural and charming; gold and silver are carefree and bright. The meeting of the ancient and modern, a ladder leading link by link to the heavens, a dream that carries you into the clouds.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-09 23:40:23', '2014-09-17 20:15:20', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
