(20555, 'SHANG XIA Opens Inaugural Worldwide First Boutique, Shanghai, 2010', '<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">SHANG XIA, a contemporary brand founded in 2008 to bring the excellence of Chinese and other Asian craftsmanship into contemporary lifestyle opens its first boutique worldwide in China on September 16, 2010.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">Inspired from the rich tradition and long history of Chinese and other Asian heritage, the boutique&rsquo;s inaugural collection will focus on the home and include furniture, decorative objects, accessories, garments and an extended experience of tea. New categories will complete this range later.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">The name SHANG XIA itself embodies the exchange between up and down, east and west, past and future, tradition and innovation, urban and nature. SHANG XIA promotes a point of view, a way of life, a Chinese modern aesthetic style. Heritage, culture, creation, dialogue and innovation merge to forge the core of SHANG XIA&rsquo;s philosophy.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">&ldquo;This is an exciting day for SHANG XIA and for the excellence and quality of Chinese craftsmanship. SHANG XIA integrates the warmth, balance and harmony of Chinese hospitality and grace,&rdquo; said Ms. Jiang Qiong Er.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">&ldquo;SHANG XIA strives for the finest quality materials and consistent craftsmanship in the range of its product offerings. The inaugural collections include &ldquo;Da Tian Di&rdquo;, zitan furniture embodying the concept of heaven and earth, &ldquo;Bridge&rdquo;, a porcelain tea set at the core of Chinese hospitality, &ldquo;Echo&rdquo; eggshell porcelain, &ldquo;Sculpture&rdquo;, hand-felted cashmere apparel, etc.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">SHANG XIA has passion and unwavering commitment to quality and the search of excellence in designing products for the home and everyday use.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">The 125 square meter store is designed by world-renown master architect Kengo Kuma. Together with SHANG XIA a concept was developed to embrace and integrate the essence of a 21st century contemporary Asian aesthetic. Using</span></p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">natural wood and sandstone combined together with high tech fiber a clean, elegant, harmonious and seamless environment has been created.</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">SHANG XIA plans to develop domestically and internationally as the market expands.</span></p>\n', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-17 23:24:09', '2014-09-17 23:24:09', NULL, 1, 'news', 0, NULL),
(20556, '“人与自然”手工艺复兴作品展，上海，2011', '<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">自然乃生命之源，</span></p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s2">浸润了中国几千年的文化和生活，</span></p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s2">是我们需要用一生时间去体会的哲学</span><span class="s3">。</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span class="s2">蒋琼耳，</span><span class="s3">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s3">」</span><span class="s2">首席执行官及艺术总监</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s1">2011-2012</span><span class="s2">年，</span><span class="s3">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s3">」</span><span class="s2">以</span><span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">人与自然</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">为主题，探寻人与自然之间的依存关系</span><span class="s3">。</span><span class="s2">品牌一周岁之时，在位于上海思南公馆的</span><span class="s3">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s3">」</span><span class="s2">之家推出</span><span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">人与自然</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">手工艺复兴作品展，呈现家具</span><span class="s3">、</span><span class="s2">茶具</span><span class="s3">、</span><span class="s2">服装</span><span class="s3">、</span><span class="s2">首饰等各个系列的新作品，以及融于其中的精湛传统手工艺</span><span class="s3">。</span><span class="s2">三层的展示空间由建筑大师隈研吾设计，以</span><span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">竹</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">与</span><span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">茶</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">为主要元素，其间手工雕塑羊绒毡服</span><span class="s3">、</span><span class="s2">竹丝扣瓷等传统手工艺现场演示，静谧</span><span class="s3">、</span><span class="s2">空灵的茶空间与香道空间，让更多的人体悟中国文化和美学精髓的传承，感受</span><span class="s1">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">绚烂而平淡</span><span class="s1">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">的生活方式</span><span class="s3">。</span></p>\n', NULL, 'cn', '2014-09-17 23:28:10', '2014-09-17 23:28:10', NULL, 1, 'news', 0, NULL);
