(20557, '「上下」全球首家零售空间正式开幕，上海，2010', '<p class="p1">\n	<span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">是一个创立于</span><span class="s3"> 2008 </span><span class="s2">年的当代中国高尚品牌</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">致力于传承中国及亚洲其他国家精湛的手工艺并将其引入当代生活</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">首家零售空间于</span><span class="s3"> 2010 </span><span class="s2">年</span><span class="s3"> 9 </span><span class="s2">月</span><span class="s3"> 16 </span><span class="s2">日在中国上海开幕</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">从中国悠久的历史文化中汲取灵感</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">以</span><span class="s3">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">家</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">为原点</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">首批作品包括家具</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">家居饰品</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">服装</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">首饰及与茶有关的物品</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">并将在以后逐渐推出更多系列</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">的名字简单却意义深远</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">它包含着时间的概念</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">上下五千年的文化积累</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">要</span><span class="s3">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">承上</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">而</span><span class="s3">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">启下</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;,</span><span class="s2">传承中国文化及美学的精髓</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">并通过创新</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">将之引向今天及未来的生活</span><span class="s1">。「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">象征着换位及对话</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">东方与西方</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">传统与现代</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">人与自然</span><span class="s1">。「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">追求天人合一</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">推崇</span><span class="s3">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">绚烂而平淡</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">的生活方式</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">将传承</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">文化</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">创新和对话融为一体</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">即成为</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">品牌的哲学核心</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s3">&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">无论是对于</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">还是对于精湛的中国传统手工艺来说</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">这都是一个让人激动的时刻</span><span class="s1">。「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">融合了中国文化的平衡与和谐</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">诠释着中国式的儒雅与热情</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">首席执行官及艺术总监蒋琼耳说</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">怀抱对上乘手工艺质量的激情</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">坚持对卓越材料品质的承诺</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">以及对创新设计的不断追求</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">打造高品质的家居和生活物品</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s2">每一件</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">的物品都选取最上等的原材料</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">使用精湛的中国及亚洲其他国家的手工艺</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">精雕细琢</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">专注于每一个细节</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">首次推出的产品包括</span><span class="s3">,&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">大天地</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">系列</span><span class="s3"> - </span><span class="s2">气度从容博大的紫檀家具</span><span class="s3">,&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">桥</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">系列</span><span class="s3"> - </span><span class="s2">融入精巧竹编技艺的白瓷茶具</span><span class="s3">,&ldquo;</span><span class="s2">天籁</span><span class="s3">&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">系列</span><span class="s3"> - </span><span class="s2">纤薄剔透的薄胎瓷作品</span><span class="s3">,&ldquo;Sculpture&rdquo;</span><span class="s2">系列</span><span class="s3"> - </span><span class="s2">手工雕塑而成无缝立体毡服</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">等等</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s2">首家零售空间由日本建筑大师隈研吾设计</span><span class="s3">,125 </span><span class="s2">平方米的空间</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">由独特的白色高科技织物营造出一个梦的氛围</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">行走其中</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">犹如在云端漫步</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">让人充满喜悦和感动</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">隈研吾在为</span><span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">设计零售空间时</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">并没有把它当做一般的空间设计</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">而是好像设计一件巨大的衣服</span><span class="s1">。</span><span class="s2">这些拥有六角形机理的白色织物</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">就好像是竹编</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">刺绣等中国传统手工艺在现代科技社会中的倒影</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">它与用于地板</span><span class="s1">、</span><span class="s2">墙面的自然纯朴的木料和石材</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">形成奇妙的对照和反差</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">却又和谐地融为一体</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n<p class="p2">\n	<span class="s1">「</span><span class="s2">上下</span><span class="s1">」</span><span class="s2">将会在中国继续发展她的品牌</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">并希望今后能与世界分享中国深厚的文化</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">精湛的传统手工艺</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">以及我们所推崇的</span><span class="s3">,</span><span class="s2">绚烂而平淡的生活方式</span><span class="s1">。</span></p>\n', NULL, 'cn', '2014-09-17 23:29:12', '2014-09-17 23:29:12', NULL, 1, 'news', 0, NULL),
