(20701, 'Minstrel', 'The SHANG XIA peasant scarf collection is a full of gaiety and good humor. The scarves are inspired by contemporary folk painting from a rural area near Shanghai: the Jinshan rustic painting school. The brushwork is simple and clean, the colors bright and eye-catching, and the modern compositions have a raw, folk energy. SHANG XIA''s work with the painters of Jinshan has allowed them to imaginatively evolve their use of materials, and to print this bright collection on silk and cashmere as commissioned by SHANG XIA.\n\nThe Minstrel collection is inspired by the painting The Entourage of Emperor Kangxi by the Qing Dynasty painter Wang Hui. It was commissioned specially for the opening of the SHANG XIA Space in Hongqiao Airport. The cloth is woven from high quality cashmere and silk, with a clear grain and a delicate feel. The colors are bold and vital. We hope this scarf will add a moment of joy to your travels, and a moment of escape to the most urban lifestyle.\n\nThe Minstrel collection is inspired by the painting The Entourage of Emperor Kangxi by the Qing Dynasty painter Wang Hui. It was commissioned specially for the opening of the SHANG XIA Space in Hongqiao Airport. The cloth is woven from high quality cashmere and silk, with a clear grain and a delicate feel. The colors are bold and vital. We hope this scarf will add a moment of joy to your travels, and a moment of escape to the most urban lifestyle.\n', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:48:58', '2014-09-18 11:51:54', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
(20702, 'Joy Dress', 'The SHANG XIA Joy collection is made from the finest Mongolian cashmere. Cut to resemble the Qipao and Chinese blouse, this collection is actually designed using the most modern tailoring technology. The trim, collar, placket and knot work buttons are machine sewed to the highest standard. The plain collection is knitted using the distinctive rice stitch while the knot work button crochet is hand stitched. The design of the Joy collection is playful, and evokes, all is illusion, and the only important thing is your personal enlightenment. This ladies’ collection provides the grace of the Qipao in the softness of woven cashmere. Easy to wear, these items will be your first call for warmth during winter.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:00', '2014-09-18 11:51:53', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
