(20705, 'Lan Yue ', 'Drawing on the humdrum perfection of the bamboo basket, SHANG XIA has created a textured leather echo of woven bamboo, with the same living grain and structure. The LAN YUE collection takes design deeper into the detail and material of the handbag than ever before. Leather and bamboo, two mature crafts, engage and blend in the LAN YUE collection, bringing new challenges for our craftsmen, and a new outlook for the handbag.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:01', '2014-09-18 11:51:53', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
(20706, 'Sun & Moon Mens Overcoat', 'The Sun & Moon collection selects the finest, softest double-sided cashmere, with a fancy hand-stitched hem that gathers the cloth into the perfect line. The result is a powerful, expressionist statement of the material. In Chinese philosophy, the sun and moon represent yang and yin. The I Ching tells us: "The sun and moon have their place in the sky." This means that the sun and moon are the way of the universe; their duality creates endless meaning in the world. The Sun & Moon collection offers the duality of a reversible coat. It can be worn either way out to suit the needs of the occasion and your changing world. The men''s collection is inspired by the traditional buttoned gown, repurposed into a greatcoat and a blazer. Both garments are presented in reserved tones, selected to speak of quiet resolve and still waters that run deep. The women''s collection adapts the classic line of the ancient shenyi gown, breaking with the old design at the shoulders, and offering either a one-piece sleeved coat or a bodywarmer. Bright as the sunshine, graceful as light, the colors were chosen for their overtones of warmth and pleasure. With Sun & Moon you are clothed in light and shade, free to float the length and breadth of this world.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:01', '2014-09-18 11:51:53', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
