(20715, 'Moonlight Overcoat', 'The SHANG XIA Moonlight collection offers a classic cut in luxurious raw silk, soft as a whisper and cool as a breeze. The seams are uniquely finished with Jali stitching, a technique named after an Indian tradition of window making. Careful detailing provides the utmost comfort in summer. In contrasting black and white, with creamy white and lustrous dark jade buttons, this is an elegant round neck shirt with an understated sheen. The ivory-white silk gives off a soft glow, rippling sensuously like a summer breeze.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:03', '2014-09-18 11:51:52', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
(20716, 'One Coat', 'The SHANG XIA One collection is made from the finest Mongolian cashmere, soft and warm. Taking inspiration from traditional Chinese tailoring, the collection refines the cardigan to its simplest form, with sleeves and body cut together from one piece of cloth. A seam elegantly joins the front and rear panels, running along the line of the sleeves and down to the lower hem forming an elegant understated pattern. The cardigan is matched with a belt but can also be worn with a tie. With its simple lines and individual detail and style, it can be an outfit in itself or be paired with other items. ', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:04', '2014-09-18 11:51:52', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
(20717, 'Sculpture Overcoat ', 'Skilled master craftsmen create these cashmere garments using techniques similar to the hand-felting of fabric for Mongolian yurts. Inspired by traditional Han dynasty clothing, this collection reflects the traditional elegance of Chinese style. “Sculpture” is cut with great precision from the rarest quality of Mongolian cashmere, then it is rubbed, rolled and formed into a seamless but form-fitting item. Two different tones of cashmere are marvelously knit into one by the weavers'' two-handed technique. They create a natural line of color around the collar, lapels and hem, giving the robe style and definition. No seams, no sew-lines, complete and unique as a cloud in the sky. Like the dawn that floods the heavens; like a hug on a winter''s day; “Sculpture”, dense and warm.', NULL, 'en', '2014-09-18 11:49:04', '2014-09-18 11:51:52', NULL, 1, 'product', 0, NULL),
